Z","msg":"咁代表hr太清閒無野做，要做埋marketing 部門嘅野先有生產力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753e15463611349d7b4820b45c9ae177eaf62d25","tid":1944632,"uid":57462,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"從來炒人請人都唔係hr 話事<br />\n一定係end user 話事<br />\n<br />\n你睇hr 比人屌到咁 就知hr 幫line食左幾多死貓"},{"pid":"5fb9f219b546f8043125ff8239cf14fcea9cd3ac","tid":1944632,"uid":191155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"hr不了，sales先幫公司做到嘢"},{"pid":"0bdb3150473c38776692ac787711ad9877942761","tid":1944632,"uid":237300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9dbd473d1e3df1bfed3f0fc66299588d01e124a","tid":1944632,"uid":189099,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c2ea133b621310f824f434c052a3e736c8015bd","tid":1944632,"uid":66528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"767864e174bcd568154031d2294d057621258ac8","tid":1944632,"uid":189099,"like":5,"dislike":32,"score":-27,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"睇咩位<br />\n有d公司有個位叫HRBP<br />\nHuman Resources Business Partner<br />\n要了解成間公司運作<br />\n咩部門適合咩人<br />\n<br />\n利申 非hr"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"其實BP即係做啲咩？？？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"HR Business Partner (HRBP) ，中文譯做人力資源業務經理或者人力資源商務伙伴，個名聽落幾型㗎。HRBP喺HR界已經出現左好一段時間，不過喺香港，可能HRBP未算太普遍，所以好多朋友都有問過呢個role到底係做乜，我嘗試用我嘅語言簡單咁介紹一下。<br />\n<br />\nHR Business Partner通常係一個獨立於HR日常Operation嘅職位（日常operation係指請人、payroll、福利、培訓等工作），佢主要嘅職責係要理解公司發展嘅策略，同時要深入唔同部門了解佢地嘅需要，從而令佢地嘅人力資源嘅安排配合到公司嘅發展。<br />\n<br />\n簡單舉個例子，例如一間賣天然薯仔嘅公司，有一日發現自己係時候要改賣基因突變薯仔，HRBP就要負責研究全盤人力資源策略。例如由於種少咗普通薯仔，就可能要諗下點樣將原本嘅人手分配去攪基因突變，又或者要諗下係咪要請多幾個基因突變專家返嚟研究，甚至要同品質檢定組研究下係咪要加強關於基因突變嘅培訓。當全盤策略定好曬之後，佢地就會將執行嘅任務交畀做日常operation嘅HR Department，例如安排招聘、培訓等工作。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mashedpatata.com/what-is-hrbp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mashedpatata.com%2Fwhat-is-hrbp%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR6d04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=f585f101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mashedpatata.com/what-is-hrbp/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:43:02.000Z","msg":"一個新business請幾多人，應該請咩人，要投入咩training 咪又係dept head 去諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者呢個位都唔應該請hr人嚟做啦，比返行業專業人士搞呢d嘢好唔好？成日呀芝呀佐搞到想請嘅人又請唔到dkgh"},{"pid":"fd27c3f0c9ce23a112b3fbac27b832e4eb1414da","tid":1944632,"uid":237300,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"524e98b945122c972d1728dc089d1445a30a9820","tid":1944632,"uid":51578,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:03:30.000Z","msg":"其實hr唔易做<br />\n細公司hr要做埋pr 團結公司同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 唔係hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"你講嗰d最撚憎嘅team building 活動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係friend 就自然friend，唔會因爲呢d濕鳩活動關係好咗囉"},{"pid":"39e899c3f7d40eea2200fd935d74c222a852638e","tid":1944632,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T06:57:42.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"b67290667d164e1e6297ae561483275cc7e2cf58","tid":1944632,"uid":226785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"年經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：做過，係admin高級版<br />\n我做得唔開心但無心唱衰呢行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9179d67a8b7e5de52b20ada461e7ba0501a8d24","tid":1944632,"uid":16507,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"Hr 都好濶，除咗請人，都有其他野要負責，好似員工福利，計糧，計假，勞工法例都要識啲<br />\n廢唔廢主要睇個人點做同公司俾唔俾資源"},{"pid":"66160a36fc2133372034dfcde603de6bcbba754c","tid":1944632,"uid":330582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"試過屌到公司d hr妹企唔穩"},{"pid":"afd6db50f6189a574d39686bb3dabd6dce72